## ‚úÖ How Cookies Work (Flow)

1.  Browser requests a page
2.  Server sends a `Set-Cookie` header
3.  Browser stores the cookie
4.  Browser sends the cookie back with future requests

<!---->

    Browser ‚Üí Request
    Server ‚Üí Set-Cookie
